# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# CareerPilot Frontend — Environment Variables
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your real values.
# All variables MUST start with VITE_ to be exposed to the browser.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── Backend API URL ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Local development:
#   VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api
#   VITE_SOCKET_URL=http://localhost:5000
#
# Production (after deploying backend to Render):
VITE_API_URL=https://careerpilot-api.onrender.com/api
VITE_SOCKET_URL=https://careerpilot-api.onrender.com
